{"tid":1561823,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"一封魚革義士寫比香港人既信［有圖］","createTime":"2019-09-11T17:49:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-12T01:30:19.000Z","uid":68738,"like":65,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":34,"replies":[{"pid":"0b282f282fcc570dab3eb73f9b62c6cd07836dd6","tid":1561823,"uid":68738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T17:49:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qZbXxcc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqZbXxcc.jpg&h=c90ba61f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n廣大市民：<br />\n<br />\n大家好。<br />\n<br />\n我是駒。16年旺角衝突案被判監3年（3個月前先判），囚友託我寫下此信，以表達對香港的支持（真的不是我的主意，我覺得自己已寫得太多，文筆差人微言輕）。囚友們對近日元朗白衣人和「克驚」（721和727）的行為感到十分憤怒，有囚友與白衣人屬同門亦不齒白衣人的暴行。而囚友對昨日有44人被控暴動罪深感痛心。囚友們支持市民大罷工，避免只用激烈的手法抗爭，和平的市民亦要用行動示威，不用前線的人犧牲太多！<br />\n<br />\nP.S.重申一次，囚友不是怕修例「拉返大陸」，而是明白中國黑獄多可怕不公。<br />\n<br />\nAndy「美國隊長」<br />\n北角蔡頭<br />\n赤柱畫王<br />\n元朗Ken<br />\n<br />\n寫於2019年8月1日<br />\n<br />\n~~~~~~~~~~~~<br />\n註:政治犯的來往信件遲一頭半個月先收到係正常的，部分信件甚至會離奇寄失 <br />\n註二: 黎緊係智駒同隊長喺獄中第一個中秋，希望大家有時間可以寫信問候下佢地😭<br />\n－－－－－－<br />\n※如果各位想寫信為隊長同駒打氣，請郵寄信件至「九龍中央郵政局郵政信箱70320號（PO Box 70320, Kowloon Central Post Office)」，我們會盡快轉送給義士💪<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/StoriesofResistance/photos/a.162025718068199/377355106535258?type=3&amp;sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2FStoriesofResistance%2Fphotos%2Fa.162025718068199%2F377355106535258%3Ftype%3D3%26sfns%3Dmo&d=y6uglPlKbSLkZz%2BcPL4okYlFrThteLnMWGuqQSPs63E%3D&h=56b73f78\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.facebook.com/StoriesofResistance/photos/a.162025718068199/377355106535258?type=3&amp;sfns=mo</a>"},{"pid":"f362e631c81c031e89fff6eeb86ba768c9ca4349","tid":1561823,"uid":76702,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T17:50:22.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"819928fe60d22ae07ef7dc4b003ae002f528d327","tid":1561823,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T17:50:38.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />出黎呀 自由閪！ <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div></strong></span></span><br />\n<strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />五大訴求 缺一不可 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></div></strong><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aPJ3iwW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaPJ3iwW.png&h=bd74ec1d&s={SIZE}\" /></div>"},{"pid":"6f0705be891d2553b857371b552299840d5df2ae","tid":1561823,"uid":114121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T17:52:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c188f3e0be3d8d6120f03cf3b4cb89e6a2f97d7e","tid":1561823,"uid":69698,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T17:54:24.000Z","msg":"多謝你地既付出"},{"pid":"aa534b78b5fe80195d1f0bf989099c09b1b13af4","tid":1561823,"uid":52417,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T17:56:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />幫你推爆佢"},{"pid":"8453c407843a8b2acf2e18b7622e5bb2bca45440","tid":1561823,"uid":305575,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T17:56:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />中秋節快樂....<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/smile.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我地一定一定唔會放棄!<br />\n祈望煲底相聚<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: navy;\">光復香港 時代革命</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"77f6d520e5162bf9dedc754f799332d3268d300a","tid":1561823,"uid":24961,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"r